<div class="content" name="LINE_PROXYREQUEST" uuid="5221aa4e-0034-4756-bbc7-35c6c14b69a2"><p>The LINE_PROXYREQUEST packet delivers a request to a <a href="489de77f-16d8-4c4f-939a-f795e8b42893#gt_624ba2cf-5c41-45cd-9334-84fbc089d34f" data-linktype="relative-path">registered proxy function
handler</a>. An application can register as proxy function handler using an
option in <a href="2759c744-e040-4c5d-b4b5-215d391f0490" data-linktype="relative-path">Open</a> packet.</p><table>
